      <title>俄罗斯天然气供应减弱，欧洲天然气价格企稳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/european-gas-prices-fall-as-russia-flows-take-steam-out-of-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于俄罗斯管道运输目前仍继续穿越乌克兰，欧洲天然气价格暂停了本月的上涨行情，趋于稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/european-gas-prices-fall-as-russia-flows-take-steam-out-of-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 08:31:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
